00:54:26,518 --> 00:54:28,000
(tense music)

1061
00:54:28,000 --> 00:54:29,788
- Kids? Timothy!

1062
00:54:29,788 --> 00:54:30,621
No!

1063
00:54:31,481 --> 00:54:33,314
Timothy!
