1068
00:54:43,430 --> 00:54:45,380
- Mm hmm. Did you get a license number?

1069
00:54:47,750 --> 00:54:50,460
- Whoever killed Larson wants me dead too.

1070
00:54:50,460 --> 00:54:53,147
- If they killed Larson because
