1076
00:55:07,120 --> 00:55:08,410
- Okay. Okay.

1077
00:55:08,410 --> 00:55:09,903
I'll attach deputy to watch you.

1078
00:55:09,903 --> 00:55:11,890
- No, then they'll be
sure I know something.

1079
00:55:11,890 --> 00:55:12,940
- You won't let me help you?

1080
00:55:12,940 --> 00:55:14,023
