1084
00:55:22,440 --> 00:55:24,450
- I'm not gonna hang around
here waiting to be killed

1085
00:55:24,450 --> 00:55:26,520
while you fill out subpoenas.

1086
00:55:26,520 --> 00:55:27,950
- Now, what does that mean?

1087
00:55:27,950 --> 00:55:30,940
- Well if I'm stuck here,
