1088
00:55:30,940 --> 00:55:32,197
- Now hold on, hold on. Just wait.

1089
00:55:32,197 --> 00:55:33,970
No use start sticking your nose.

1090
00:55:33,970 --> 00:55:36,646
Oh, oh boy.

1091
00:55:36,646 --> 00:55:39,646
(suspenseful music)

1092
00:56:00,768 --> 00:56:03,300
