1099
00:56:28,460 --> 00:56:30,750
Questions about Archie's land.

1100
00:56:30,750 --> 00:56:33,740
About how strange it is that
I'm the only builder in town

1101
00:56:33,740 --> 00:56:35,770
who owns Archie's land.

1102
00:56:35,770 --> 00:56:38,093
- She's just making a pest
of herself, that's all.

1103
00:56:38,093 --> 00:56:40,020
I mean, ain't gonna do her no good.

1104
00:56:40,020 --> 00:56:42,370
- She's also asking (coughs)

1105
00:56:42,370 --> 00:56:45,040
about a little girl visiting Archie.

1106
00:56:45,040 --> 00:56:47,900
How do you suppose she put
together Tina with Archie?

1107
00:56:47,900 --> 00:56:49,100
You answer me that, huh?

1108
00:56:50,008 --> 00:56:51,258
- I don't know.

1109
00:56:56,289 --> 00:56:58,597
(suspenseful music)

1110
00:56:58,597 --> 00:57:00,310
(Martha gasps)

1111
00:57:00,310 --> 00:57:02,600
- Hotter than a whore's breath in here.

1112
00:57:02,600 --> 00:57:04,530
- Take your rustic homilies and get out

