business, disrupting our lives.

1119
00:57:22,180 --> 00:57:24,660
If you want to know
anything about Archie Maddox

1120
00:57:25,590 --> 00:57:27,380
or about who owns his land

1121
00:57:28,600 --> 00:57:29,433
you come to me.

1122
00:57:29,433 --> 00:57:30,850
You understand that?

1123
00:57:31,883 --> 00:57:33,040
- What about that snake,

1124
00:57:33,040 --> 00:57:35,450
was that supposed to scare me outta town?

1125
00:57:35,450 --> 00:57:36,800
Don't you get it?

1126
00:57:36,800 --> 00:57:38,870
If I try to leave town,
