00:59:10,419 --> 00:59:12,172
- Look, there's something else.

1158
00:59:12,172 --> 00:59:14,489
- - What?
- Came from Linda's kids.

1159
00:59:14,489 --> 00:59:16,210
They used to play near
Archie Maddox's house.

1160
00:59:16,210 --> 00:59:17,480
- Yeah, the guy Larson came to see.

1161
00:59:17,480 --> 00:59:19,200
- Yeah, and Archie would chase 'em away

1162
00:59:19,200 --> 00:59:21,400
