1575
01:24:21,610 --> 01:24:22,443
- Timothy!

1576
01:24:23,721 --> 01:24:24,554
Emily!

1577
01:24:31,393 --> 01:24:33,404
They've taken my kids!

1578
01:24:33,404 --> 01:24:35,304
- They'll be returned after I testify.

1579
01:24:36,910 --> 01:24:39,930
- It says after you
testify you saw nothing.

1580
01:24:39,930 --> 01:24:40,763
