1587
01:24:49,690 --> 01:24:50,523
Do you hear me?

1588
01:24:50,523 --> 01:24:51,460
Do you hear me?

1589
01:24:51,460 --> 01:24:54,017
- Listen, you stay by the phone.

1590
01:24:54,017 --> 01:24:59,017
