1591
01:25:07,257 --> 01:25:08,326
- [Linda] Where are you going?

1592
01:25:08,326 --> 01:25:09,159
Martha!

1593
01:25:20,146 --> 01:25:24,610
(doorbell rings)
(knocking at door)

1594
01:25:24,610 --> 01:25:25,730
- Mrs. Potter.

1595
01:25:25,730 --> 01:25:26,563
Mrs. Potter.

1596
01:25:27,470 --> 01:25:30,211
Mrs. Potter who painted this?

1597
01:25:30,211 --> 01:25:33,090
- (scoffs) Well wasn't Gauguin.

1598
01:25:33,090 --> 01:25:36,350
- Tina Maddox only with forged papers.

1599
01:25:36,350 --> 01:25:39,540
She's registered at
Rosedale Hall a Katie Bass.

1600
01:25:39,540 --> 01:25:41,513
