1601
01:25:42,780 --> 01:25:44,770
But you took her to see her father, Archie

1602
01:25:44,770 --> 01:25:47,243
under her real name, Tina Maddox.

1603
01:25:50,070 --> 01:25:51,570
Archie loved that little girl.

1604
01:25:53,140 --> 01:25:54,943
But he never told anyone about her.

1605
01:25:56,110 --> 01:25:57,833
He and his wife were divorced.

1606
01:25:58,690 --> 01:26:00,790
Tina lived with her mother until she died.

1607
01:26:02,126 --> 01:26:04,303
And Archie had to put her an institution.

1608
01:26:08,250 --> 01:26:10,913
They just soak up love
when they're like that.

1609
01:26:13,120 --> 01:26:14,570
My son was-
- I know.

1610
01:26:14,570 --> 01:26:17,470
I know. And I'm so very, very sorry.

1611
01:26:17,470 --> 01:26:19,230
But now that's over.

1612
01:26:19,230 --> 01:26:22,000
Your husband murdered Archie Maddox.

1613
01:26:22,000 --> 01:26:23,480
And he stole his land.

1614
01:26:23,480 --> 01:26:24,500
And if we hadn't found Tina,

1615
01:26:24,500 --> 01:26:26,090
he might've gotten away with it.

1616
01:26:26,090 --> 01:26:27,563
That land belongs to her.

1617
01:26:28,580 --> 01:26:30,610
- Archie's death was an accident.

1618
01:26:30,610 --> 01:26:31,610
- Maybe.

1619
01:26:31,610 --> 01:26:33,590
But the second one wasn't.

1620
01:26:33,590 --> 01:26:35,520
I saw Larson killed. I saw Eddie do it.

1621
01:26:35,520 --> 01:26:37,440
And your husband was
standing right next to him.

1622
01:26:37,440 --> 01:26:39,590
Now they've kidnapped
my sister's children.

1623
01:26:41,990 --> 01:26:43,760
- They've gone too far to turn back now.

1624
01:26:43,760 --> 01:26:44,634
- Stop it.

1625
01:26:44,634 --> 01:26:45,750
(Hilda gasps)
(glass shatters)

1626
01:26:45,750 --> 01:26:49,143
Two children you love are going
to die unless you speak up.

1627
01:26:51,361 --> 01:26:53,861
(tense music)

1628
01:27:16,842 --> 01:27:19,509
(ominous music)

1629
01:27:23,280 --> 01:27:24,330
- What have you done?

1630
01:27:27,962 --> 01:27:29,545
What have you done?

1631
01:27:35,351 --> 01:27:37,037
(gunfire pops)

1632
