- Dangerous man, Jake.

1633
01:27:42,660 --> 01:27:44,542
- Who the hell is that?

1634
01:27:44,542 --> 01:27:47,042
- You better go on outta here.

1635
01:28:04,730 --> 01:28:05,820
- Linda, no.

1636
01:28:05,820 --> 01:28:06,653
- Eddie!

1637
01:28:07,590 --> 01:28:09,130
Where are they, Eddie?

1638
01:28:09,130 --> 01:28:10,324
- Easy, there was never no danger.

1639
01:28:10,324 --> 01:28:11,820
It was just like a big game to 'em, honey.

1640
01:28:11,820 --> 01:28:13,393
Okay? Take it easy, sweetie.

1641
01:28:13,393 --> 01:28:14,643
- Mommy! Mommy!

1642
01:28:39,340 --> 01:28:40,173
- Eddie!

1643
01:28:47,730 --> 01:28:49,680
Take your family in the trailer, Eddie.

1644
01:28:51,820 --> 01:28:53,570
Get 'em on in there so we can talk.

1645
01:28:55,360 --> 01:28:56,930
- We're leaving now.

1646
01:28:56,930 --> 01:28:59,140
Linda, get the kids in the truck.

1647
01:28:59,140 --> 01:28:59,973
You too.

1648
01:29:04,020 --> 01:29:06,200
- Do what I tell ya, Eddie.

1649
01:29:06,200 --> 01:29:07,033
Not this time.

1650
01:29:08,343 --> 01:29:09,693
- Hold it right there, son.

1651
01:29:16,600 --> 01:29:20,200
- You know it's funny you
callin' me son like that.

1652
01:29:20,200 --> 01:29:22,490
'Cause I always looked at you as a father.

1653
01:29:22,490 --> 01:29:24,780
Even when you was gonna dump me.

1654
01:29:24,780 --> 01:29:28,873
You and the others gonna let
me take the fall for all of ya.

1655
01:29:30,136 --> 01:29:33,303
And still I looked at you as a father.

1656
01:29:34,626 --> 01:29:35,726
And them as my family.

1657
01:29:36,690 --> 01:29:37,877
- We were just trying to motivate you.

1658
01:29:37,877 --> 01:29:41,103
- Oh, you got me real motivated,
Mr. Potter, real motivated.

1659
01:29:43,690 --> 01:29:44,523
One question.

1660
01:29:45,780 --> 01:29:47,500
Being that I owe you and all,

1661
01:29:47,500 --> 01:29:49,440
was you gonna ask me to
kill my kids for you too?

1662
01:29:49,440 --> 01:29:51,140
- Don't do anything stupid, Eddie.

1663
01:29:53,147 --> 01:29:55,624
- I'm gonna do something
smart for a change.

1664
01:29:55,624 --> 01:29:57,320
In fact, it's gonna hurt you all the more.

1665
01:29:57,320 --> 01:29:59,843
'Cause it was dumb ole Eddie
Pick that done it to y'all.

1666
01:30:00,729 --> 01:30:01,871
(gunfire pops)

1667
01:30:01,871 --> 01:30:04,538
(all screaming)

1668
01:30:08,280 --> 01:30:09,613
- Daddy!
- Eddie!

1669
01:30:12,261 --> 01:30:15,286
(gunfire pops)

1670
01:30:15,286 --> 01:30:16,302
(Doyle yells)

1671
01:30:16,302 --> 01:30:19,135
