1679
01:30:54,550 --> 01:30:55,620
- I know.

1680
01:30:55,620 --> 01:30:57,501
What's gonna happen to Eddie?

1681
01:30:57,501 --> 01:30:59,140
- He'll testify against
Jake and the others,

1682
01:30:59,140 --> 01:31:02,470
they'll be bargaining from
murder one down to manslaughter,

1683
01:31:02,470 --> 01:31:04,693
most likely, maybe if he's lucky.

1684
01:31:06,350 --> 01:31:07,770
But the town will be dead to him

1685
